file reading classes :
- file -- represents a file or a directory
- scanner -- reads the file(that is line by line)
- buffer reader -- this helps in reading the file or large files in a faster pace


now we are learning  about the file writing classes in java'
- file writer --  writing a class in java
- printwriter -- easy file output with println
- bufferedwriter --effiecient writing

for the exception in file i/o uses we will come across exceptions we have to use the try catch block
